# .mailmap — canonical identity for each contributor.
#
# Format (one per line):
#   Canonical Name <canonical@email>
#   Canonical Name <canonical@email>  <other@email>
#   Canonical Name <canonical@email>  Other Name <other@email>
#
# Reference: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap
#
# This file collapses commits made under multiple email addresses /
# spellings into a single contributor in `git log`, `git shortlog`,
# and GitHub's contributor stats.
#
# Add yourself when you contribute under more than one email
# (e.g. workplace + personal, or GitHub's noreply alias).

